{"tid":2357584,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"公司智能坐墊監控員工 離座即上傳","createTime":"2021-01-07T13:40:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T15:16:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5ee8d788571739d87eaf7bc190ddeac19a0603aa","tid":2357584,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:40:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210107/KEPHQ742JZBS3BFFOMMMZUXTYA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210107%2FKEPHQ742JZBS3BFFOMMMZUXTYA%2F&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6zyWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=75b50809\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210107%2FKEPHQ742JZBS3BFFOMMMZUXTYA%2F&h=de5c1f6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210107/KEPHQ742JZBS3BFFOMMMZUXTYA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n公司智能坐墊監控員工 離座即上傳<br />\n<br />\n浙江杭州有公司派發智能坐墊（圖，箭嘴示）予員工，稱可監察心跳、呼吸、坐姿等，更會溫馨提示員工適時起身活動筋骨。豈料該坐墊同時如同「監視器」，網民發現坐墊竟將數據上傳到人力資源部，令人「有種上班被扒光了的感覺，就像坐牢」。公司則解畫，稱坐墊僅用於內部測試，數據不計入考核、考勤。專家就質疑科技監控手段已走火入魔，衍生私隱問題之餘，亦帶來反效果。<br />\n<br />\n網名「蘋果橙子妹妹」的網民在論壇分享公司派發的智能坐墊，指起初同事均覺實用，但後來發現工作情況，包括離開座位時間都會被上傳，令其大嘆「體驗真的很差」。<br />\n<br />\n涉事的杭州「荷博物聯」隨後發聲明，指智能坐墊是公司新產品，用於監測使用者的健康狀態，目前仍處於研發階段。公司派給員工試用，屬研究用途，而數據會保密；人力資源部員工未遵從私隱保護條例，已予嚴重警告。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6sC4QQRy0jMVdYHqmZkh2mixeyg=/494x659/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KU6QTYC4MVDZNBFPACX7VAT6QQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6sC4QQRy0jMVdYHqmZkh2mixeyg%3D%2F494x659%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKU6QTYC4MVDZNBFPACX7VAT6QQ.jpg&h=3f7c287c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n方保僑︰走火入魔<br />\n<br />\n內地以高科技監控打工仔已非新鮮事，之前「快手」在洗手間設計時器，及江蘇南京曾向清道夫派發定位智能手環，都引發過爭議。<br />\n<br />\n香港資訊科技商會榮譽會長方保僑則指，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n界面新聞/《都市快報》"},{"pid":"404062b3bd6f6c209fd7e295e7fbb95ae48bf2ce","tid":2357584,"uid":18999,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:44:49.000Z","msg":"搵舊重野放係座位咪得"},{"pid":"7180f887ab7bbbb9579dce7a88b757820efde1b0","tid":2357584,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:50:01.000Z","msg":"幾好喎又"},{"pid":"f19e70e965d8c3a58ec9744ef89d54271e779eef","tid":2357584,"uid":71335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:50:11.000Z","msg":"坐住去廁所 周圍走"},{"pid":"5fcf489cd1a6a65a81833ce672850af7b6475e91","tid":2357584,"uid":40369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"404062b3bd6f6c209fd7e295e7fbb95ae48bf2ce","tid":2357584,"uid":18999,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:44:49.000Z","msg":"搵舊重野放係座位咪得"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:51:09.000Z","msg":"佢可以check 埋心跳"},{"pid":"421a49d1e31f7019322991fd365e9e2941f373ed","tid":2357584,"uid":28181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:53:03.000Z","msg":"中國人是要管的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"773ea09c5d3e324d2e55964e95160150c41b77c8","tid":2357584,"uid":179288,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:53:41.000Z","msg":"乾脆一人一部霍金輪椅咪算啦"},{"pid":"7d80b67bd0fc30d7ba0e9aeb61475d152c8e5c78","tid":2357584,"uid":53601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fcf489cd1a6a65a81833ce672850af7b6475e91","tid":2357584,"uid":40369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"404062b3bd6f6c209fd7e295e7fbb95ae48bf2ce","tid":2357584,"uid":18999,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:44:49.000Z","msg":"搵舊重野放係座位咪得"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:51:09.000Z","msg":"佢可以check 埋心跳"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:55:41.000Z","msg":"䀫眼瞓即時穿煲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd47b7f62b98b56d5f2eafcdd7d93da0f8f7f529","tid":2357584,"uid":293937,"like"